19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:21,067
<i>The rebels elect a new leader!</i>

20
00:00:21,150 --> 00:00:22,693
<i>With their training complete,</i>

21
00:00:22,777 --> 00:00:25,780
<i>Obi-Wan and Anakin have left Ahsoka
on Onderon</i>

22
00:00:25,863 --> 00:00:30,076
<i>to monitor and advise the rebels as
they continue to strike Separatist targets</i>

23
00:00:30,159 --> 00:00:32,245
<i>under the command of Steela Gerrera.</i>

24
00:00:33,538 --> 00:00:35,957
<i>Facing an escalation of rebel attacks,</i>

25
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:40,378
<i>the Separatists have sent reinforcements
to strengthen their hold on the city of Iziz</i>

26
00:00:40,461 --> 00:00:43,214
<i>as the battle for the planet unfolds.</i>

27
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:45,591
Oh!

28
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,718
Yummy, yummy!

29
00:01:17,582 --> 00:01:19,250
Looks like more reinforcements.

30
00:01:19,584 --> 00:01:22,169
Small droid convoy
leading a multi-troop transport,

31
00:01:22,336 --> 00:01:23,921
<i>with an AAT bringing up the rear.</i>

32
00:01:24,005 --> 00:01:25,089
Copy.

33
00:01:43,608 --> 00:01:46,027
Ah ! It's an ambush !
We need reinforcements!

34
00:01:59,832 --> 00:02:01,709
No! No!

35
00:02:23,856 --> 00:02:26,442
Do not be afraid, brothers and sisters!

36
00:02:27,568 --> 00:02:29,070
We mean you no harm.

37
00:02:36,285 --> 00:02:37,411
It's time.

38
00:02:47,797 --> 00:02:49,632
<i>People of Onderon,</i>

39
00:02:50,091 --> 00:02:52,927
<i>the time has come
to take back our freedom.</i>

40
00:02:53,803 --> 00:02:55,680
<i>We have all been deceived.</i>

41
00:02:56,097 --> 00:03:00,976
<i>King Rash is a traitor who has sold
Onderon to the Separatists for the crown.</i>

42
00:03:01,644 --> 00:03:03,771
But Onderon is ours.

43
00:03:04,105 --> 00:03:06,774
We need your strength
to reclaim our planet

44
00:03:07,024 --> 00:03:09,610
and restore our sovereignty
under our true king,

45
00:03:10,611 --> 00:03:11,821
King Dendup.

46
00:03:20,913 --> 00:03:23,332
The terrorists are no longer a nuisance

47
00:03:23,958 --> 00:03:25,918
but a threat to Onderon.

48
00:03:26,711 --> 00:03:30,005
It is only a matter of time
before they are all eliminated.

49
00:03:30,297 --> 00:03:33,217
How much longer
before they plunge us into chaos?

50
00:03:33,551 --> 00:03:35,886
It seems they're only targeting
the droid army.

51
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:39,849
If you allow the Royal Onderon Militia
to assume control of security,

52
00:03:39,932 --> 00:03:42,309
the terrorists may stop and discuss terms.

53
00:03:42,727 --> 00:03:45,604
You will assume nothing, General Tandin.

54
00:03:45,688 --> 00:03:47,898
With their coordinated attacks
and weapons,

55
00:03:47,982 --> 00:03:51,152
it is possible they are finding sympathy
within your own ranks.

56
00:03:51,652 --> 00:03:53,195
The threat is external.

57
00:03:53,362 --> 00:03:56,115
And your reinforcements have done little
to stop them.

58
00:03:56,449 --> 00:03:59,869
We will not negotiate with terrorists.

59
00:04:00,202 --> 00:04:02,621
They fear diplomacy.
They embrace mayhem.

60
00:04:03,164 --> 00:04:04,707
What do we know about them?

61
00:04:10,671 --> 00:04:14,008
We've identified Steela Gerrera
as the woman in the hologram.

62
00:04:14,091 --> 00:04:16,552
Her brother Saw is also part of the group,

63
00:04:16,719 --> 00:04:19,305
as well as the fugitive criminal
Lux Bonteri.

64
00:04:19,513 --> 00:04:22,349
The late Senator Mina Bonteri's son?

65
00:04:22,641 --> 00:04:24,018
Yes, my lord.

66
00:04:24,351 --> 00:04:25,603
Why was I not told of this?

67
00:04:26,854 --> 00:04:28,022
You just were.

68
00:04:28,856 --> 00:04:29,940
Enough!

69
00:04:30,191 --> 00:04:32,818
It's clear that Dendup is behind this.

70
00:04:33,194 --> 00:04:35,362
We mustn't allow
his followers any momentum.

71
00:04:35,821 --> 00:04:38,741
Justice must come swiftly, without mercy.

72
00:04:38,824 --> 00:04:39,909
Bring him in!

73
00:04:49,210 --> 00:04:50,419
What now?

74
00:04:51,128 --> 00:04:54,840
Your supporters have begun
to publicly decry my reign.

75
00:04:55,132 --> 00:04:58,052
Am I still to believe
you're not behind their attacks?

76
00:04:58,803 --> 00:05:00,888
You must order them to surrender.

77
00:05:01,597 --> 00:05:02,890
Impossible.

78
00:05:03,182 --> 00:05:06,769
I have been isolated and alone,
without visitors,

79
00:05:06,977 --> 00:05:08,771
confined to my prison.

80
00:05:08,854 --> 00:05:13,734
Again, the will of the people is theirs,
not mine.

81
00:05:16,529 --> 00:05:20,324
Well, then we shall see
what the will of the people is made of.

82
00:05:25,538 --> 00:05:27,998
Okay, guys, put it in the back with the rest.

83
00:05:28,082 --> 00:05:29,333
Steela!

84
00:05:30,251 --> 00:05:33,212
They're executing King Dendup tomorrow
in Yolahn Square.

85
00:05:33,295 --> 00:05:34,380
Where did you hear this?

86
00:05:34,463 --> 00:05:36,423
Malgan Market. The merchants.

87
00:05:36,507 --> 00:05:39,051
The Separatists are saying
he's behind our attacks.

88
00:05:39,718 --> 00:05:41,136
More lies.

89
00:05:42,221 --> 00:05:44,765
They're making him an example
to humiliate us.

90
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:48,978
Maybe, but their efforts
could work against them.

91
00:05:49,061 --> 00:05:51,605
Executing him
would only make him a martyr.

92
00:05:52,106 --> 00:05:55,442
We can't let him die.
We have to break him out somehow.

93
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:58,696
No, we should wait until he's in public.

94
00:05:58,779 --> 00:05:59,989
At the execution.

95
00:06:00,447 --> 00:06:01,866
That's where they'd expect it.

96
00:06:02,283 --> 00:06:04,451
I know. But this is our moment.

97
00:06:04,493 --> 00:06:06,996
We'll save him for all of Iziz to witness.

98
00:06:07,204 --> 00:06:08,539
We don't have much time.

99
00:06:08,789 --> 00:06:10,499
They're counting on us to show up.

100
00:06:11,792 --> 00:06:12,835
Where are you going?

101
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,003
Trust me.

102
00:06:15,004 --> 00:06:16,130
Stop!

103
00:06:17,172 --> 00:06:18,674
Let me take care of this.

104
00:06:19,174 --> 00:06:20,801
This isn't about you.

105
00:06:21,176 --> 00:06:23,137
We can't afford a reckless move right now.

106
00:06:23,888 --> 00:06:25,973
Yeah? Go write a speech about it.

107
00:06:28,392 --> 00:06:30,060
You have to weigh the risk.

108
00:06:31,228 --> 00:06:32,980
That's why I'm going alone.

109
00:06:38,861 --> 00:06:39,904
Follow him.

110
00:06:49,496 --> 00:06:50,998
Steela.

111
00:06:52,833 --> 00:06:55,878
Saw is strong. He'll be fine.

112
00:06:56,587 --> 00:07:00,007
He's always been brash. Never thinks.

113
00:07:00,382 --> 00:07:04,011
He doesn't realize by leaving us,
he's hurting us.

114
00:07:05,012 --> 00:07:06,180
We need a plan.

115
00:07:07,932 --> 00:07:11,518
They bring King Dendup through
the east entrance of Yolahn Square.

116
00:07:13,604 --> 00:07:15,522
Security will be tight.

117
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:19,109
And rescuing him will not be easy.

118
00:07:21,528 --> 00:07:22,863
Lux,

119
00:07:22,905 --> 00:07:24,698
please don't look at me like that.

120
00:07:25,366 --> 00:07:27,034
Forgive me. I'm sorry, I...

121
00:07:27,368 --> 00:07:28,535
Listen,

122
00:07:28,869 --> 00:07:30,746
I just need to be alone right now.

123
00:07:31,747 --> 00:07:33,415
Gather everyone to go over the plan.

124
00:07:34,541 --> 00:07:35,751
Of course.

125
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:51,892
<i>I sense fear in you, Ahsoka.</i>

126
00:07:52,601 --> 00:07:54,061
The rebels are divided.

127
00:07:54,228 --> 00:07:57,898
If they try to rescue the king now,
I'm afraid we might lose them.

128
00:07:58,107 --> 00:08:00,025
<i>We cannot control their fate.</i>

129
00:08:00,401 --> 00:08:01,568
It's just...

130
00:08:01,694 --> 00:08:04,279
They're risking their lives to save just one.

131
00:08:04,947 --> 00:08:07,282
<i>Do not underestimate the King's power.</i>

132
00:08:07,408 --> 00:08:10,452
<i>He represents hope
and is critical to their success.</i>

133
00:08:15,708 --> 00:08:17,710
I feel responsible for them.

134
00:08:17,918 --> 00:08:20,087
<i>I know you do, Snips. But remember,</i>

135
00:08:20,212 --> 00:08:22,381
<i>purpose must come before feelings.</i>

136
00:08:22,881 --> 00:08:24,133
I know, Master.

137
00:08:24,258 --> 00:08:26,260
<i>Step in only if you must.</i>

138
00:08:26,385 --> 00:08:30,764
<i>But remember, if this experiment
is to become an effective strategy,</i>

139
00:08:30,806 --> 00:08:32,558
<i>they must learn to survive on their own.</i>

140
00:08:33,475 --> 00:08:36,103
Yes, Master Kenobi, I understand.

141
00:09:39,333 --> 00:09:40,417
Uh...

142
00:09:40,501 --> 00:09:41,585
Hey!

143
00:09:47,091 --> 00:09:48,133
My lord.

144
00:09:49,843 --> 00:09:51,011
Who are you?

145
00:09:51,345 --> 00:09:52,763
I'm Saw Gerrera.

146
00:09:53,347 --> 00:09:54,765
What do you want?

147
00:09:55,015 --> 00:09:56,350
Your freedom, Sire.

148
00:09:56,475 --> 00:09:59,311
You're to be executed tomorrow,
but I'm getting you out of here.

149
00:09:59,812 --> 00:10:02,272
The people of Onderon need your help.

150
00:10:02,856 --> 00:10:03,941
Stand up!

151
00:10:05,484 --> 00:10:08,529
Are you one of the meddlers
creating disorder,

152
00:10:08,654 --> 00:10:11,031
interfering in the affairs of the throne?

153
00:10:11,156 --> 00:10:14,368
Only to restore Your Kingship
as the rightful ruler.

154
00:10:15,536 --> 00:10:17,037
I see.

155
00:10:18,789 --> 00:10:22,459
This was all my doing. I opened the door.

156
00:10:22,709 --> 00:10:25,295
That's why the Separatists are here.

157
00:10:25,963 --> 00:10:28,465
I was faced with a difficult choice.

158
00:10:28,674 --> 00:10:31,301
To join the Republic or the Confederacy.

159
00:10:31,885 --> 00:10:33,262
Both are corrupt,

160
00:10:33,345 --> 00:10:37,641
but I had to pick a side
before one was chosen for me.

161
00:10:38,642 --> 00:10:40,686
Except I chose neither.

162
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:43,605
Now is the time to take back Onderon.

163
00:10:43,689 --> 00:10:47,234
Our movement is gaining momentum,
it has the backing of the Jedi.

164
00:10:47,985 --> 00:10:49,319
Jedi?

165
00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:51,155
Yes, Sire.

166
00:10:51,613 --> 00:10:54,658
I've been waiting a long time for this.

167
00:10:55,742 --> 00:10:58,495
Follow me, Sire. Onderon awaits.

168
00:11:01,165 --> 00:11:02,499
One-way shield.

169
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:25,063
Do any of you have questions?

170
00:11:25,981 --> 00:11:28,650
It's a risky plan, but it's our best shot.

171
00:11:28,984 --> 00:11:31,320
Ahsoka, will you join us?

172
00:11:31,612 --> 00:11:32,821
I can't.

173
00:11:32,905 --> 00:11:35,824
I've already been more involved
than the Council wanted.

174
00:11:35,908 --> 00:11:39,036
I'm afraid I've been instructed
to sit this one out.

175
00:11:40,829 --> 00:11:42,080
They have Saw!

176
00:11:42,164 --> 00:11:44,416
He's alive.
But I watched them take him away.

177
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,504
We have to save him.

178
00:11:49,588 --> 00:11:51,256
-Yeah !
-Yes!

179
00:11:55,886 --> 00:11:56,970
No.

180
00:11:58,889 --> 00:12:00,974
We have to save King Dendup.

181
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:04,144
We don't have time or the bodies
to do both.

182
00:12:04,561 --> 00:12:05,646
He's your brother.

183
00:12:05,729 --> 00:12:08,565
That's what Saw would want.
What he would expect.

184
00:12:09,233 --> 00:12:12,527
And I expect the same
from everyone in this room.

185
00:12:13,695 --> 00:12:15,239
I know it's a hard choice,

186
00:12:15,322 --> 00:12:16,615
but I agree.

187
00:12:16,949 --> 00:12:19,076
Purpose must come before feelings.

188
00:12:35,592 --> 00:12:37,719
Where are the other terrorists?

189
00:12:38,303 --> 00:12:41,181
Onderon is our system.

190
00:12:41,265 --> 00:12:42,391
Not yours.

191
00:12:51,566 --> 00:12:52,651
Enough!

192
00:12:56,530 --> 00:13:00,450
We have to keep him alive.
He is a direct link to the terrorists.

193
00:13:00,951 --> 00:13:04,037
-You pity him.
-I pity your ignorance.

194
00:13:04,913 --> 00:13:07,332
You can control the people of Onderon,

195
00:13:07,624 --> 00:13:10,627
but you won't sustain it against their will.

196
00:13:11,003 --> 00:13:13,714
What you're doing guarantees
others will take his place.

197
00:13:14,381 --> 00:13:16,591
They, too, will suffer.

198
00:13:16,883 --> 00:13:18,802
Then the war is lost.

199
00:13:20,137 --> 00:13:21,305
You have strong tactics,

200
00:13:21,388 --> 00:13:25,100
but it's unfortunate
you cannot calculate a different approach.

201
00:13:37,404 --> 00:13:40,324
Here, drink. It will give you strength.

202
00:13:42,743 --> 00:13:45,454
The Separatists have
very little compassion or patience

203
00:13:45,579 --> 00:13:47,414
for things that stand in their way.

204
00:13:48,498 --> 00:13:49,583
Hmm.

205
00:13:49,666 --> 00:13:52,127
We have a duty
to protect what's ours, General.

206
00:13:52,586 --> 00:13:54,629
A duty once entrusted to you.

207
00:13:54,838 --> 00:13:57,841
I thought you depleted your arrogance
with Kalani.

208
00:13:59,843 --> 00:14:01,803
It replenishes every hour.

209
00:14:01,928 --> 00:14:03,013
Ah...

210
00:14:03,764 --> 00:14:06,266
King Rash is the crowned head of Onderon.

211
00:14:06,475 --> 00:14:09,603
What's yours is his.
And he will do with it as he pleases.

212
00:14:10,145 --> 00:14:12,105
Dendup is the true king.

213
00:14:12,773 --> 00:14:14,441
Are you following his orders?

214
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,943
We take orders from no one.

215
00:14:17,652 --> 00:14:21,114
Aligning yourself with the past
does not bode well for your future.

216
00:14:21,198 --> 00:14:23,116
We share the same future.

217
00:14:23,283 --> 00:14:26,828
We can sit here as free men
or servants of the Separatists.

218
00:14:27,371 --> 00:14:28,663
I am free,

219
00:14:28,789 --> 00:14:31,291
while you have chosen
to become a terrorist.

220
00:14:31,375 --> 00:14:33,960
I'm not a terrorist, I'm a patriot.

221
00:14:34,002 --> 00:14:36,463
And resistance is not terrorism.

222
00:14:38,465 --> 00:14:40,133
King Dendup chose his people

223
00:14:40,258 --> 00:14:43,470
instead of taking a side
in the intergalactic war.

224
00:14:43,970 --> 00:14:46,473
Separatists have taken over Onderon

225
00:14:46,681 --> 00:14:48,183
because we let them.

226
00:15:20,715 --> 00:15:22,634
As your king,

227
00:15:22,884 --> 00:15:26,054
I present to you Ramsis Dendup,

228
00:15:26,221 --> 00:15:28,223
not as a former king,

229
00:15:28,557 --> 00:15:30,142
but as a criminal

230
00:15:30,392 --> 00:15:34,229
sponsoring terrorist acts
against the people of Onderon.

231
00:15:34,855 --> 00:15:37,023
But fear not, good citizens,

232
00:15:37,065 --> 00:15:39,734
as your leader and protector,

233
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:43,029
I will see that you are safe
from such villainy.

234
00:15:43,572 --> 00:15:45,490
He has betrayed you,

235
00:15:45,532 --> 00:15:49,327
and today he will pay
for those treasonous deeds

236
00:15:49,494 --> 00:15:50,996
with his life!

237
00:15:53,957 --> 00:15:56,460
Your people will see you
into the next world.

238
00:15:57,127 --> 00:15:59,212
May you find forgiveness there.

239
00:16:17,814 --> 00:16:18,899
Time to die.

240
00:16:28,867 --> 00:16:30,577
Wait for my signal.

241
00:16:31,036 --> 00:16:32,704
Ready weapons.

242
00:16:38,043 --> 00:16:39,211
Not yet.

243
00:16:41,254 --> 00:16:42,380
Now!

244
00:16:54,351 --> 00:16:55,769
Come on ! Go, go, go!

245
00:16:58,063 --> 00:16:59,856
- Come with us.
- Blast them!

246
00:17:15,872 --> 00:17:17,165
Follow me!

247
00:17:19,834 --> 00:17:22,003
This way! Come on, let's go!

248
00:17:35,976 --> 00:17:37,686
Surrender now or die.

249
00:17:43,024 --> 00:17:45,485
It's over. Do as they say.

250
00:17:52,492 --> 00:17:54,953
Calm yourselves! The threat is over.

251
00:17:55,328 --> 00:17:59,833
See for yourselves as these traitors
all endure the same punishment.

252
00:18:04,254 --> 00:18:05,839
Good try, sis.

253
00:18:19,352 --> 00:18:20,854
Ready weapons.

254
00:18:25,025 --> 00:18:27,402
- No!
- They're innocent!

255
00:18:27,527 --> 00:18:28,570
Let them go!

256
00:18:28,862 --> 00:18:31,615
This snake will not strike again.

257
00:18:31,948 --> 00:18:33,450
- Stop!
- What?

258
00:18:34,951 --> 00:18:38,371
The only snake I see, Sire, is you.

259
00:18:49,382 --> 00:18:51,426
-Traitor!
-I was.

260
00:18:51,885 --> 00:18:53,094
Not anymore.

261
00:18:59,517 --> 00:19:01,061
What are you doing, General?

262
00:19:05,565 --> 00:19:06,650
Go.

263
00:19:18,578 --> 00:19:19,954
- Let them through !
- Make way!

264
00:19:20,163 --> 00:19:21,748
Everyone, go with them.

265
00:19:22,165 --> 00:19:23,583
-But, sir...
-Go!

266
00:19:29,756 --> 00:19:31,591
What now, General?

267
00:19:31,716 --> 00:19:34,761
As soon as you release me,
you'll be shot dead.

268
00:19:43,311 --> 00:19:44,396
Jedi!

269
00:19:44,938 --> 00:19:46,231
General, follow me.

270
00:19:51,861 --> 00:19:54,322
After them ! Kill them ! Kill them!

271
00:19:54,406 --> 00:19:57,242
-Dendup is the true king !
-We want the Separatists gone!

272
00:20:15,135 --> 00:20:16,553
Why now?

273
00:20:17,137 --> 00:20:19,264
It was time for a new approach, my lord.

274
00:20:21,391 --> 00:20:23,309
Do I have your loyalty?

275
00:20:23,977 --> 00:20:25,478
And that of the army.

276
00:20:26,312 --> 00:20:27,647
You also have ours.

277
00:20:28,106 --> 00:20:30,483
With your rule, our numbers will grow.

278
00:20:31,109 --> 00:20:32,902
Thanks, child.

279
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:35,989
Your mother would be proud.

280
00:20:36,489 --> 00:20:37,782
Thank you, my lord.

281
00:20:38,283 --> 00:20:43,329
We must first win the will of the people.
That is the only way.

282
00:20:43,997 --> 00:20:47,333
The Separatists will assemble their forces.

283
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:51,796
Count Dooku will want me dead
more than ever.

284
00:20:52,839 --> 00:20:56,301
Then we'll have to teach them
another lesson, together.

285
00:21:01,181 --> 00:21:02,348
Ahsoka,

286
00:21:02,390 --> 00:21:04,017
I knew you couldn't resist a good fight.

287
00:21:04,851 --> 00:21:06,895
Am I becoming that predictable?

288
00:21:07,353 --> 00:21:08,688
Only to me.

289
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:15,528
The Separatists definitely know
we're backing the rebels.

290
00:21:16,029 --> 00:21:19,824
<i>Then prepare yourself.
The real fight is about to begin.</i>

291
00:21:20,366 --> 00:21:22,368
Will you be able to send some help?

292
00:21:22,577 --> 00:21:24,871
<i>That's up to the Council, Ahsoka.</i>

293
00:21:24,895 --> 00:21:29,895
http://hiqve.com/

